      "start": "0x493F",
      "end": "0x494F",
      "kind": "data",
      "width": 16,
      "comment": "palette_top \u2014 only [0..11] are read by the IRQ; [12..15] are present but unused. DEFAULT bytes are the scenario-1 palette (red/yellow). Scenarios 2-4 are loaded by Loader2 PROCL34 / PROCL56 / PROCL78 which `READ T%?&493F` 16 bytes each from DATA at lines 1160 / 1180 / 1200 (dispatched from L%=?&9D at lines 940-970)."
    },
    {
