  "comments": {
    "0x4900": "Common prologue saves A/X/Y. Tests User VIA IFR bit 7 (T1 IRQ pending) \u2192 if so, jumps to irq_palette_split_b for the bottom palette. Otherwise tests sysVIA IFR bit 7 (vsync); if not vsync, chains immediately. Vsync path re-primes UVIA T1 (BC34 cycles \u2248 mid-frame), then writes palette_top[0..11] \u2192 &FE21.",
    "0x497E": "Called by Loader2 line 1000 (CALL&497E). Saves the prior IRQ1V at zp_old_irq_vec_lo/hi, installs irq_palette_split as the handler, primes UVIA T1L-H + IER + ACR for the mid-frame timer."
  },
